dc_description_s: Cover title. Wood block print. Oriented with north to the right. Relief shown pictorially. Cadastral map. Includes list of points of interest. Extension pasted on the bottom of map. 1 map: col.; 76 x 89 cm, folded in covers 18 x 13 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
